data.title: About: Karipey Rural District
data.meta_description: Karipey Rural District (Persian: دهستان كارئ پي) is a rural district (dehestan) in Lalehabad District, Babol County, Mazandaran Province, Iran. At the 2006 census, its population was 31,761, in 8,094 families. The rural district has 56 villages.
